## Finale API Efficiency Rules
- Max **3 concurrent workers** in scanning loops
- **100ms pause** between SKU dispatches
- **Product filter** on all `orderViewConnection` calls: `product: ["/${accountPath}/api/product/${sku}"]`
- **Combined GraphQL**: use field aliases to merge receipts + shipments + open POs into 1 request
- **REST-first exclusion**: check `isManufactured`/`isDropship` BEFORE expensive GraphQL calls

## Dropship Exclusion List (both panels ‚Äî server-side)
Autopot, Printful, Grand Master, HLG, Evergreen, AC Infinity
Regex in `resolveParty()`: `/autopot|printful|grand.?master|\bhlg\b|horticulture lighting|evergreen|ac.?infinity/i`
These are dropship-only. They MUST NOT appear in ReorderPanel or PurchasingPanel.

## Cron (America/Denver)
7:30 AM Mon-Fri build risk | 8:00 AM daily summary | 8:01 AM Fri weekly | Every 15 min AP | Hourly ads | Every 30 min PO sync
